These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, folk, rock
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | folk | funk | electronic | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, lizard, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | rabbit | lizard | rat | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, magic-tricks, writing, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | writing | skydiving | magic-tricks | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | car | trike | tram | motorbike |

 #################################

 
